snippet.title: Vroomies Trailer - Swipe, Tap, Race! Available on Android and iOS
snippet.description:
Vroomies is a racing game tailor made for touch controls! Using simple swipes and taps, you’ll race your Vroomie to victory against your adorably fierce competition!

Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nightlight.vroomies

iOS: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/vroomies/id6465789264

🏆 Championship Mode 🏆

Put your racing mettle to the test in 4 Championships! Race to the top of the standings, unlocking Upgrades and Challenges for a fresh experience every time you play. It'll take a good strategy and quick thumbs to make it to the top - do you have what it takes?

🌎 Global Leaderboards 🌎

See where you stack up against the fastest Vroomies in the world!

👍 Play Your Way 👍

Experiment with 12 unique Upgrades and 3 Vroomie Types to create the perfect build for each Challenge
